HEADWORD: Watcher
<hw>Watch"er</hw> <pr>(-⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
watches; one who sits up or continues; a diligent observer;
specifically, one who attends upon the sick during the night.</def>⟦br⟧
